  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter in a Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add shallots, garlic, carrots, and celery. Cook, stirring occasionally, until vegetables are tender, about 8 minutes.",
    "Add tofu, red wine, beef broth, tomato paste, and thyme. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring to a boil, then cover and transfer to the oven.",
    "Bake at 300°F (150°C) for 25-30 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened and the tofu is cooked through.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
